<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Challenge Created - Eighteen</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #bbe4e9;
      --primary-dark: #8fd0d7;
      --accent: #F72585;
      --light: #F8F9FA;
      --dark: #212529;
      --success: #4CC9F0;
      --gray: #6C757D;
    }
    
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    
    body {
      background-color: var(--light);
      color: var(--dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .message-box {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--dark);
    }
    
    p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    strong {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: var(--dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background-color: var(--primary-dark);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="message-box">
      <h2>Challenge Created!</h2>
      <p>We've sent an invitation to <strong><%= friendEmail %></strong> and will notify you when they accept.</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">Back to Homepage</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>